  "description": "Add lots of blocks and new variations.",
  "body": "<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HBdK32L.png\" width=\"1110\" height=\"327\" /></p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-redactor=\"1\">This mod (Fabric) allows you to add lots of different Minecraft blocks.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-redactor=\"1\">It also adds some variations like vertical blocks and new quarter blocks.<br /><br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ebNj8m8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"356\" height=\"50\" /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-redactor=\"1\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-redactor=\"1\">These are new variations that don't exist in Minecraft.<br />They will allow you to detail your constructions enormously.<br /><br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ifihZTO.png\" width=\"704\" height=\"315\" />\n<div data-redactor=\"1\"><br />There are also stairs and slabs (vertical) for all blocks of Minecraft. A dream come true.</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-redactor=\"1\"><br /><strong>Additional blocks and items</strong></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-redactor=\"1\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-redactor=\"1\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sLrhkst.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"760\" /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-redactor=\"1\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-redactor=\"1\">You also have the option of adding grass to the dirts slabs.<br />As well as other small details...</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-redactor=\"1\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-redactor=\"1\"><strong style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\"><b>Support:</b></strong><a title=\"Discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/nx8yUPY\"><br /><img class=\"bbCodeImage wysiwygImage\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6BQW5lz.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>",
